{"tid":2002651,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"「回帶」貨幣互換三年送左200億俾中國","createTime":"2020-05-05T10:08:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-05T10:26:07.000Z","uid":200288,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f34144bdee1443eadd0871987b4de934c826c6ee","tid":2002651,"uid":200288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T10:08:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7uyMShT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7uyMShT.png&h=81289163&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n按照今日匯率計 <br />\n4000億人民幣淨係得4390.9億港幣<br />\n但三年前港共俾左4700億港幣出去<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">即係白白送咗210億俾中共<br />\n除開700萬人 <br />\n港共送咗我地香港人每人3000蚊俾中共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"5ec54c16008f8a5f3970713ea1bfcf67e211f2f9","tid":2002651,"uid":200288,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T10:09:31.000Z","msg":"每人俾中共強姦左一部Iphone SE<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca7e8857d45c5761872e9e3aafa99c026d771c2a","tid":2002651,"uid":200288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T10:10:32.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"98dfc6f8f25e6f1fd5764043162b2f39389afb9c","tid":2002651,"uid":200288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T10:10:46.000Z","msg":"2/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddfd870267129eaa88f96c4935213e93daf1a3c5","tid":2002651,"uid":200288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T10:10:58.000Z","msg":"3/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69dd75020c38740d53b19a842741295ec90aefcd","tid":2002651,"uid":53062,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T10:11:17.000Z","msg":"NMSL國專登貶人民幣值，成功呃到唔少國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8638d8f0881beb45d090a81a74